{
  "stem": "9478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was working two years without a penny as a helper for the bus driver.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I got my license.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when got my license, I couldn't believe that a little man like me-- a little Jew like me-- can drive a bus of 30, 40 people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we were only two Jewish bus drivers in the whole province.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other guy was killed, and I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But all my dream was to help out my mother, because she was widow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She never remarried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had chances to go away to United States, because I had a grandfather in New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But she says no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Either we go all of the four of us or nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Michel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He left Korzec in the '30s-- 1932, 1933.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were struggling in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he used to send us in sometimes $5, $10.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the way my mother made a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was Michel Tarach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they change the name to Glazer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were in Zhytomyr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no-- Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember lots of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if I will tell you the history, so I don't think you'll have enough tape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you major things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, major things was then we were living in a little town surrounded with Ukrainians-- murderers, gangsters, you know-- it was scary to go out on the street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we lived--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would cut off your ear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would smash you, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Always were some incidents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we tried to stay at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the problem was this-- then we were on the border of Russia and Poland up until 1939.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1939, the Russian came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they divided Poland on two parts-- one part up to Bug, and the other part is Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was German, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
